{
  "stem": "945.1",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "The director, I remember, was a name-- a gentleman by the name of Zabolotni, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] who was a very nice man.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "I'll never forget him.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "What I'm trying to say is that on the one hand when I came home, life was depressed.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And we feared the system.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And when I went to school, I was elated by the fact that I could learn and learn in my own language.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "That was the paradox.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And so life went on until one day.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And I remember that day.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "It was on a Sunday.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "It was June the 22, 1941.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] We had amongst the kids a soccer game.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And we were involved in that-- in our game.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And we saw planes overhead.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And we saw trucks running fast with sirens and with flags waving.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "And we soon found out that Germany had declared war on the Soviet Union.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] Of course, all Jewish, able-bodied men were quickly taken to the Russian army.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And our situation was very uncertain.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "We feared that soon we will be overrun by the Germans and by the Romanians again.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "A lot of people rescued themselves or tried to rescue themselves by fleeing with the Russian authorities into the Soviet Union before the Germans came in.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "The local Ukrainian fascists started to smell blood.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "And they were, of course, out in full force to take advantage of whatever served them.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "And so a new era of uncertainty, war, started.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "OK.",
      "word_count": 1
    }
  ],
